## Best Practices

### General

- Keep documentation up to date
- Use clear language
- Include examples
- Link related docs
- Version documentation

### Code Comments

- Explain why, not what
- Document edge cases
- Note assumptions
- Include examples
- Reference related code

### API Documentation

- Clear descriptions
- Complete parameters
- Response examples
- Error scenarios
- Authentication requirements

### Architecture Documentation

- Clear diagrams
- Component relationships
- Data flow
- Security considerations
- Performance notes

